description: This data set presents Metropolitan Statistical Areas (MSAs) that are participating in the Comprehensive Care for Joint Replacement Model, a proposed model to support better and more efficient care for beneficiaries undergoing the most common inpatient surgery for Medicare beneficiaries: hip and knee replacements.
